S.FORM: dadiw balucu' nu bayu' tina dadiw sa, namakay cacay a iga nu Amilika "balucu' nu bayu'". u sulit tina dadiw izaw ku ahebalay a bayu' i baucu' nu maku itiza inayi' ku salaedan a kakitizaan izawtu ku likat nu cilal hatnisadikud amana malaheci ku nizateng pabeli' nu taw izaw ku bihid mikitinay numakuay mucelak balaki i mungangaw kalusalupiku i sakauzip kaluzazan i sakauzip kaulakakangalalan kalumalawpes caay katalaw tu sasadakayan inayi' ku kakutizaan amana talabu matengil kaku ku sani' i baaday ulaulangan miawaw takuwanan caykaydih matineng hacica ku baad nu hezek makucaw tu bali mulitemuh tu tapelik paculil tu baybay caay maungan u pakayzaan i balucu' u nikangelu' atu lakalak a culil nu sakauzip haca maenapay i nikatezaan saayaway inayi' ku lalum k baduku uyzasa amahedaw ku nizateng nu maku haca aizawtu ku maseneng uyzasa izaw ku azteng nu maku i salabuay nu bayu' ilabu' nu balucu' nu maku
